      "Preheat the oven to 180ºC (160ºC fan) or gas mark 4.",
      "Mash the ricotta and beat well with the egg yolks.",
      "Stir in the flour, sugar, cinnamon, grated lemon rind, and the rum, mixing well. This can be done in a food processor.",
